 fstab-decode \- run a command with fstab-encoded arguments
 
 .SH SYNOPSIS
-\fBfstab-decode\fR \fICOMMAND\fR [\fIARGUMENT\fR]...
+\fBfstab-decode\fR \fICOMMAND\fR [\,\fIARGUMENT\fR \&.\|.\|.\&]
 
 .SH DESCRIPTION
 .B fstab-decode
